text: Jessie Ellen Wadworth was an archer from Great Britain. She was born on 12 November 1863 and died on 8 July 1936. Wadworth competed at the 1908 Summer Olympics.Jessie WadworthJessie Ellen WADWORTH == References == Category:1863 births Category:1936 deaths Category:British archers Category:Olympians for Great Britain
